'''''Golden Dreams''''' was a modified [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub]] [[Transport/Legends|medium transport]] in [[Drea Renthal]]'s [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] fleet. The ship was fairly large, but lightly shielded and poorly armed. Its role was to carry some of Renthal's [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunters]] into battle. ''Golden Dreams'' would launch the fighters, then fall back to a safe distance while they and the dedicated warships of Renthal's fleet did the fighting.

